    <string name="privacy_policy_text">
    <![CDATA[
    <b>1. Introduction</b><br/>
    GenAI Expense Tracker is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines how your data is collected, used, and safeguarded when you use the app.<br/><br/>

    <b>2. Data Collection</b><br/>
    We collect the following data when you use the application:<br/>
    • <b>Email address</b> – used for authentication via Firebase Authentication.<br/>
    • <b>Income and expense entries</b> – stored securely in Firestore to track your financial activity.<br/>
    • <b>Profile photo</b> – optionally uploaded by you for personalization.<br/><br/>

    <b>3. Data Usage</b><br/>
    The data collected is used strictly for the following purposes:<br/>
    • To visualize your income and expense trends.<br/>
    • To generate financial insights via AI (Gemini API).<br/>
    • To produce downloadable financial reports in PDF format.<br/><br/>

    <b>4. Data Sharing</b><br/>
    Your personal data is <b>never sold or shared</b> with third-party marketers. Data may only be shared:<br/>
    • With Firebase services (as part of secure cloud storage).<br/>
    • As required by law (e.g., in response to lawful requests).<br/><br/>

    <b>5. Storage and Security</b><br/>
    • All data is stored in Google Firebase Cloud Firestore.<br/>
    • Reports are uploaded to Firebase Storage securely.<br/>
    • Communication with Firebase is protected using HTTPS encryption.<br/><br/>

    <b>6. Your Rights</b><br/>
    You have full control over your data:<br/>
    • You may request deletion of your account and associated data.<br/>
    • You can update or modify your entries anytime.<br/>
    • You may sign out or uninstall the app to stop data collection.<br/><br/>

    <b>7. Consent</b><br/>
    By using this app, you consent to this Privacy Policy and agree to the collection and use of your data as described.<br/><br/>

    <b>8. Contact</b><br/>
    For any privacy-related concerns or data deletion requests, please contact us at:<br/>
    <i>kawpeelpandey@gmail.com</i><br/>
